sections.title: About
sections.content: Dynamic and results-driven software developer with 2 years of experience in designing, developing, and deploying scalable web applications using Nest.js and Node.js. Proficient in building RESTful APIs and implementing best practices in software development. Strong background in TypeScript, JavaScript, MongoDB, and PostgreSQL, with a passion for creating efficient and maintainable code. Experienced in collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.
